tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE email_engagement_data (
  email_id UUID NOT NULL,
  open_timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  click_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  user_id INT NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (email_id, user_id)
)

CREATE TABLE email_engagement (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  email_address TEXT NOT NULL,
  open_status BOOLEAN,
  click_status BOOLEAN,
  engagement_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE EmailEngagements (
    engagement_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    contact_id INT,
    campaign_id INT,
    engagement_type VARCHAR(50),
    engagement_time TIMESTAMP
);
